[[SalesforceDeveloperAccountSetup-SalesforceDeveloperAccountSetup]]
== Salesforce Developer Account Setup

To set up a free developer Salesforce account:

[[SalesforceDeveloperAccountSetup-1.Register]]
==== 1. Register

Go to http://www.developerforce.com/events/regular/registration.php  and
register.

 

[[SalesforceDeveloperAccountSetup-2.ResetYourSecurityToken]]
==== 2. Reset Your Security Token

After logging in to Salesforce, go to Setup.

image:/documentation/download/attachments/66060978/SFDC-Setup-1.png?version=1&modificationDate=1305663668418[image]

Then, Select "Reset Security Token" from My Personal Information>Reset
My Security Token

image:/documentation/download/attachments/66060978/SFDC-ResetSecurityToken.png?version=1&modificationDate=1305663668427[image]

You'll receive an email with your new Security Token.

Salesforce uses password+securitytoken for API authentication.
